wift 5.3, iOS 14, macOS 11 (Big Sur), tvOS 14, watchOS 7."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WidgetKit"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"StoreKit Testing"},{"type":"text","text":", and more."}],"kind":"article"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC19-712-Advances-in-Networking-Part-1":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc19-712-advances-in-networking-part-1","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC19-712-Advances-in-Networking-Part-1","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Keep up with new and evolving networking protocols and standards by leveraging the modern networking frameworks on all Apple platforms and following best practices for efficiency and performance. In this session, learn about Low Data Mode, Combine in URLSession, WebSocket, and improvements to network mobility.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Advances in Networking, Part 1","role":"sampleCode"},"https://x.com/SarthakKhillon":{"url":"https:\/\/x.com\/SarthakKhillon","identifier":"https:\/\/x.com\/SarthakKhillon","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"X\/Twitter","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"X\/Twitter"},"WWDC20-10111-tcp_stats":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-tcp_stats","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-tcp_stats.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10047-Enable-encrypted-DNS":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10047-enable-encrypted-dns","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10047-Enable-encrypted-DNS","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"When people access the web within your app, their privacy is paramount. Safeguard that information by leveraging encrypted DNS across our platforms to deliver private and secure connectivity within your app. Discover how you can use system DNS settings to connect to encrypted servers or enable encrypted DNS within an app using standard networking APIs.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Enable encrypted DNS","role":"sampleCode"},"WWDC20-10111-ipv6_stats":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-ipv6_stats","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-ipv6_stats.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/skhillon":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/skhillon","images":[{"type":"card","identifier":"skhillon.jpeg"},{"type":"icon","identifier":"skhillon.jpeg"}],"abstract":[{"text":"No Bio on GitHub","type":"text"}],"title":"Sarthak Khillon (19 notes)","role":"sampleCode","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/skhillon","kind":"article"},"../10047":{"url":"..\/10047","identifier":"..\/10047","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Enable Encrypted DNS","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"Enable Encrypted DNS"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC20.jpeg":{"identifier":"WWDC20.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://github.com/skhillon":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/skhillon","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/skhillon","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"GitHub","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"GitHub"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Contributions are welcome!","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"Contributions are welcome!"},"WWDC20-10111-http2_stats":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-http2_stats","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-http2_stats.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC20-10111-tls_stats":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-tls_stats","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-tls_stats.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3_mac":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3_mac","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3_mac.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC20-10111-dns":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-dns","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-dns.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3":{"identifier":"WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDC20-10111-experimental_http3.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"skhillon.jpeg":{"identifier":"skhillon.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/skhillon.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2018/714/":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2018\/714\/","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2018\/714\/","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Optimizing Your App for Today’s Internet","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"Optimizing Your App for Today’s Internet"},"https://developer.apple.com/wwdc20/10111":{"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc20\/10111","identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/wwdc20\/10111","checksum":null,"type":"download"},"https://multipath-tcp.org/":{"url":"https:\/\/multipath-tcp.org\/","identifier":"https:\/\/multipath-tcp.org\/","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"https:\/\/multipath-tcp.org","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"https:\/\/multipath-tcp.org"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC20-10110-Support-local-network-privacy-in-your-app":{"url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc20-10110-support-local-network-privacy-in-your-app","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC20-10110-Support-local-network-privacy-in-your-app","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Local network privacy provides added transparency when apps connect to devices on a person’s home network. If your app interacts with devices using Bonjour or other local networking protocols, you must add support for local network privacy permissions in iOS 14. Learn more about the new permission flow and follow along as we guide you through the necessary steps to update your app. We’ll also provide you with some best practices to help you create a frictionless privacy experience.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","title":"Support local network privacy in your app","role":"sampleCode"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community."}],"images":[{"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","title":"WWDC Notes"},"skhillon":{"identifier":"skhillon","alt":"Profile image of Sarthak Khillon","type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/skhillon.jpeg","traits":["1x","light"]}]}}}